name: BluetoothRemoteGATTDescriptor.uuid
description: The BluetoothRemoteGATTDescriptor.uuid read-only property returns the UUID of the characteristic descriptor, for example '00002902-0000-1000-8000-00805f9b34fb' for theClient Characteristic Configuration descriptor.
content:
This is an experimental technology
Check the Browser compatibility table carefully before using this in production.

The BluetoothRemoteGATTDescriptor.uuid read-only property returns the UUID of the characteristic descriptor, for example'00002902-0000-1000-8000-00805f9b34fb'for theClient Characteristic Configurationdescriptor.
